{"word":"ἀμνημονέω","slug":"ἀμνημονέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀμνημονέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀμνήμων'><el>ἀμνήμων</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to be unmindful</i>, <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>to make no mention of, not speak of</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; so, <el>ἀμν. τι περί τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}